    <problem workspace="1.5in">
        <statement>
            <p>
                Use <m>B</m> to solve the system <m>A \vec{x} = \vec{b}</m>
                <me></me>

                <me>\vec{x} = \framebox{$\phantom{$\begin{bmatrix} a \amp a \amp a \amp a \\ b  \\ c \end{bmatrix}$}$ }</me>
